tyle=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">訴</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"75e0ea2fb1fa8e6212077e468baf71a6aece054c","tid":1539743,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">求</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"418412122367b66791189c84b607e35b901de1c3","tid":1539743,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ad8d7268829ce1dd5e63264f6a7a6903092c1f6","tid":1539743,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f7c4cae2e78f13b13ee4019ac9c1500b4a291fe","tid":1539743,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b3e9c119be1cd617d064361e54df71316bdd9c41","tid":1539743,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2f0534953135219de2d29b357138480042f1745a","tid":1539743,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港、洗腦教育\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"}]}